					<![CDATA[
						 <p>It was actually inspired by that specific SCP (Taffeta linked me to it)!</p> <p>Part of the idea behind Adelaide is that in some alt-universe, Project Rhodes was about time-travel rather than alt-universes. Project your consciousness into the past every time you die, rather than your whole <em>body</em>!</p> 
				 	]]>
