					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7193941#post-3936385</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7193941/it-s-the-end-of-the-world-as-you-know-it-and-i-feel-fine#post-3936385</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 28 Aug 2018 07:32:59 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>The Great Hippo</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3938622</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Thanks! And it doesn't exist (as far as I'm aware); the closest thing I know of is <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/multi-u-101">Multi-U</a>, which explores alternate universes, but doesn't examine dead (or dying) worlds to determine how best to avoid the apocalypse.</p> <p>(also notable and not touched on in this story: All personnel in the OEI are survivors from worlds that ended)</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
